comments: Capela (ATL) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he moves to imminently guard an opponent that cuts through the lane.
Murray (ATL) swipes down and makes clean contact with the ball prior to incidental contact occurring with Barrett's (NYK) arm after his gather.
Capela (ATL) rests his hands on Grimes' (NYK) body with no force as he establishes position in his path.
Johnson (ATL) maintains a legal guarding position during Randle's (NYK) drive to the basket.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Randle (NYK) loses the ball out of bounds.
Grimes (NYK) initiates contact with Young's (ATL) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Barrett (NYK) and Hunter (ATL) briefly engage and immediately disengage as their arms become entangled during the pick.
Young (ATL) initiates contact with Brunson's (NYK) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Barrett (NYK) contests Hunter's (ATL) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Grimes (NYK) continues moving forward into Young (ATL), initiating body contact that affects his SQBR as he recovers the loose ball.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Brunson (NYK) passes the ball out of bounds.
Johnson (ATL) commits a take foul on Randle (NYK).
Barrett (NYK) brushes Young's (ATL) back as he defends the driving shot attempt and the contact is marginal.
Capela (ATL) initiates contact with Randle's (NYK) arm and affects Randle's ability to pass.
Randle (NYK) crosses the plane of the free throw line before the free throw makes contact with the rim.
Johnson (ATL) initiates contact with Randle's (NYK) arm and affects Randle's SQBR.
